}}'''Limited-time events''' are scenarios that happen for a set period of time, depending on the day, holiday and what's in the news. These do not have an effect on the character's life.

== List of events ==
=== Current Events ===
These are real-life events that happen in the news, and are shortly available in BitLife for a period of time. The player can choose how their character responds to it.
